               <msContents>
                  <summary>Chants called Zǝmmare, Zǝmmare, ዝማሬ፡ (f<locus target="#1r">fols. 1r, </locus>-35r); <locus target="#36r">36r, </locus> secondary note of ownership; Chants called Mäwaś‘ǝt Chants, መዋሥዕት። (f<locus target="#37r">37r</locus>-58v)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="35r" facs="003">Fols 1r–35r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2610Zemmar">Zǝmmāre</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጽሒፈ፡ አንቀጽ፡ ዝማሬ፡ ግዕዝ፡ ዓራራይ፡ እስመ፡ ለዓለም፡ ምሕረቱ፡ በ፪ወተፈነወ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ከመ፡ ይስብክ፡ ምጽአቶ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="37r" to="58v" facs="039">Fols 37r–58v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1990Mawase">Mawāśǝʾǝt</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">መዋሥዕት፡ ፲፬ እግዚኦ፡ መኑ፡ የሐድር፡ ውስተ፡ ጽላሎትከ። ዓቢየ፡ ነቢየ፡ ዮሐንስሃ፡ አስአልነ፡ ያስተምሕር፡ በእንቲአነ፡ ሣህልከ፡ ይኩን፡ ላእሌነ፡ ዘይገብር፡ ከመዝ፡ ወኢይትሐወክ፡ ለዓለም <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
